StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetAllEthnic]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
AS
SELECT -1 AS ID, ETHNIC_CODE AS Code, ETHNIC_LONG_DESCRIPTION AS Descrip.on, ETHNIC_ABBREVEATION, ETHNIC_SHRT_DESCRIPTION FROM [dbo].[ETHNIC] WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE ETHNIC_CODE != 'Z' ORDER BY [ETHNIC_SHRT_DESCRIPTION]
